window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Bluesman: musician, magician, lethal killer. Thrown into our world from a parallel universe, the Bluesman seeks to save the Earth from being overrun by the horrid, mutated creatures that came with him. Armed with magic, skill, and his companion, Scotch, he faces these monsters hoping to create a peaceful world for all.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>The Bluesman</i> contains all nine original stories that make up The Bluesman series.</p>"; 
